      • getSerializationMarshaller

        public static <T extends java.io.Serializable> Marshaller<T> getSerializationMarshaller()
        Returns a Marshaller that uses Java Serialization. Works for any type that implements Serializable, but is not space-efficient for boxed primitives like Long or Double.

      • getStringMarshaller

        public static Marshaller<java.lang.String> getStringMarshaller()
        Returns a Marshaller for Strings. They will be encoded in UTF-8.
